{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013ci4hbx6ZKhx7o7XKXK26s","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01DFM7abm5cHUP5xhCMoTBHu","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__roster__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/CHANGELOG.md","content":"# Migration Changelog: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Quarkus\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:34:00Z] [info] Project Analysis\n- Identified multi-module Jakarta EE project with 5 modules: roster-common, roster-ejb, roster-web, roster-appclient, roster-ear\n- Application deployed as EAR on Open Liberty 24.0.0.12\n- Technologies: EJB 4.0 (Stateful, Singleton, Startup), JPA 3.0 with EclipseLink, JAX-RS, JSF, CDI\n- H2 in-memory database via Liberty DataSource\n- JPA static metamodel generated by EclipseLink annotation processor\n- 18 Java source files across 5 modules\n- REST API endpoints for Leagues, Teams, and Players CRUD operations\n- DataInitializer seeds 4 canonical leagues (L1-L4) at startup\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:34:30Z] [info] Migration Strategy\n- Flatten multi-module EAR project into single Quarkus JAR module\n- Replace EJB annotations with CDI equivalents\n- Replace @EJB injection with @Inject\n- Replace EJBException with RuntimeException\n- Replace @Remote interface with plain interface\n- Replace @Singleton/@Startup with @ApplicationScoped + @Observes StartupEvent\n- Replace @Stateful with @ApplicationScoped + @Transactional\n- Replace static metamodel (Player_, Team_, League_) with string-based Criteria API\n- Drop JSF beans (PlayerBean, LeagueBean, TeamBean) - REST-only in Quarkus\n- Drop application client (RosterClient) - not applicable in Quarkus\n- Replace Open Liberty server.xml with Quarkus application.properties\n- Replace EclipseLink with Hibernate ORM (Quarkus default)\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:35:00Z] [info] Dependency Update - pom.xml\n- Removed multi-module parent POM structure (modules: roster-common, roster-ejb, roster-web, roster-appclient, roster-ear)\n- Removed Open Liberty BOM (io.openliberty.features:features-bom:24.0.0.12)\n- Removed liberty-maven-plugin\n- Removed jakarta.jakartaee-api:10.0.0\n- Removed jakarta.jakartaee-web-api:10.0.0\n- Removed EclipseLink modelgen processor\n- Removed maven-ejb-plugin, maven-ear-plugin, maven-war-plugin\n- Removed com.h2database:h2 direct dependency (now via quarkus-jdbc-h2)\n- Added Quarkus BOM (io.quarkus.platform:quarkus-bom:3.17.8)\n- Added quarkus-rest-jackson (JAX-RS REST with Jackson JSON)\n- Added quarkus-hibernate-orm (JPA via Hibernate)\n- Added quarkus-jdbc-h2 (H2 database driver)\n- Added quarkus-arc (CDI implementation)\n- Added quarkus-narayana-jta (JTA transaction support)\n- Added quarkus-smallrye-health (health checks for smoke tests)\n- Added quarkus-maven-plugin for build lifecycle\n- Changed packaging from POM to JAR\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:35:30Z] [info] Project Restructure\n- Removed roster-common/ module directory\n- Removed roster-ejb/ module directory\n- Removed roster-web/ module directory\n- Removed roster-appclient/ module directory\n- Removed roster-ear/ module directory\n- Created flat src/main/java/ source tree with all classes consolidated\n- Created src/main/resources/ for Quarkus configuration\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:36:00Z] [info] Entity Migration\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/League.java\n  - Changed from property-based JPA access to field-based access\n  - Added @Inheritance(strategy = InheritanceType.SINGLE_TABLE) for entity hierarchy\n  - Initialized teams collection to ArrayList to prevent NPE\n  - Removed redundant @Id from getter, placed on field\n  - Removed redundant @OneToMany from getter, placed on field\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/Player.java\n  - Changed to field-based JPA annotations\n  - Initialized teams collection to ArrayList\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/Team.java\n  - Changed to field-based JPA annotations\n  - Initialized players collection to ArrayList\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/SummerLeague.java\n  - No functional changes, copied as-is\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/entity/WinterLeague.java\n  - No functional changes, copied as-is\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:36:30Z] [info] EJB to CDI Migration - RequestBean\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/request/RequestBean.java\n  - Replaced @Stateful @LocalBean with @ApplicationScoped\n  - Replaced @PersistenceContext with @Inject for EntityManager\n  - Removed Serializable implementation (not needed for CDI)\n  - Replaced @PostConstruct CriteriaBuilder initialization with lazy getter method getCb()\n  - Added @Transactional to all mutating methods (createPlayer, addPlayer, removePlayer, dropPlayer, createTeamInLeague, removeTeam, createLeague, removeLeague)\n  - Replaced all EJBException throws with RuntimeException\n  - Replaced all static metamodel references (Player_.position, Team_.city, League_.id, etc.) with string-based Criteria API (\"position\", \"city\", \"id\", etc.)\n  - Added null check in getPlayer() to return null instead of NPE\n  - Added null check in getTeam() to return null instead of NPE\n  - Added null safety in copyPlayersToDetails()\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:36:45Z] [info] EJB to CDI Migration - DataInitializer\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/request/DataInitializer.java\n  - Replaced @Singleton @Startup with @ApplicationScoped\n  - Replaced @PostConstruct with @Observes StartupEvent (Quarkus lifecycle)\n  - Replaced @TransactionAttribute(TransactionAttributeType.REQUIRED) with @Transactional\n  - Replaced @PersistenceContext with @Inject for EntityManager\n  - Added import for io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:37:00Z] [info] Interface Migration - Request\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/request/Request.java\n  - Removed @Remote annotation (EJB remote interface not applicable in Quarkus)\n  - Removed jakarta.ejb.Remote import\n  - Interface now serves as a plain CDI bean interface\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:37:15Z] [info] JAX-RS Resource Migration - RosterResource\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/RosterResource.java\n  - Replaced @EJB with @Inject for Request bean injection\n  - Replaced EJBException catch with RuntimeException catch\n  - Replaced hasIncorrectSportCause(EJBException) with hasIncorrectSportCause(RuntimeException)\n  - Removed jakarta.ejb.EJB and jakarta.ejb.EJBException imports\n  - Added jakarta.inject.Inject import\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:37:20Z] [info] JAX-RS Application\n- File: src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/RosterApplication.java\n  - Retained @ApplicationPath(\"\") for root context path\n  - No functional changes needed\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:37:30Z] [info] DTO and Utility Classes\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/util/PlayerDetails.java\n  - Added setters for Jackson JSON deserialization\n  - No other changes\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/util/TeamDetails.java\n  - No changes needed\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/util/LeagueDetails.java\n  - No changes needed\n- File: src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/util/IncorrectSportException.java\n  - No changes needed\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:37:45Z] [info] Dropped Files (Not Migrated)\n- roster-web/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/PlayerBean.java (JSF bean - not applicable)\n- roster-web/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/LeagueBean.java (JSF bean - not applicable)\n- roster-web/src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/TeamBean.java (JSF bean - not applicable)\n- roster-web/src/main/webapp/*.xhtml (JSF views - not applicable)\n- roster-web/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml (Liberty web config - not applicable)\n- roster-web/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml (CDI config - Quarkus uses arc)\n- roster-ejb/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml (replaced by application.properties)\n- roster-ear/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml (Liberty config - not applicable)\n- roster-appclient/ (entire app client module - not applicable)\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:38:00Z] [info] Configuration Migration\n- File: src/main/resources/application.properties\n  - quarkus.http.port=8080 (equivalent to Liberty httpPort=9080, changed to standard 8080)\n  - quarkus.datasource.db-kind=h2 (equivalent to Liberty H2 DataSource)\n  - quarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:h2:mem:roster;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1 (same as original)\n  - quarkus.hibernate-orm.database.generation=drop-and-create (equivalent to persistence.xml)\n  - quarkus.package.jar.type=uber-jar (for simple deployment)\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:38:15Z] [info] Dockerfile Migration\n- Changed build command from: mvn clean install -pl roster-ear -am\n  to: mvn clean package -DskipTests\n- Changed run command from: mvn liberty:run -pl roster-ear\n  to: java -jar target/roster-1.0.0-runner.jar\n- Added requests to pip install for smoke test HTTP calls\n- Added EXPOSE 8080\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:38:30Z] [info] Smoke Tests Generated\n- File: smoke.py\n  - 19 tests covering all REST API endpoints\n  - Tests: health check, league CRUD, team CRUD, player CRUD\n  - Tests: query endpoints (by position, salary range, city, sport, league)\n  - Tests: relationship operations (add/drop player to team)\n  - Tests: seeded data verification (canonical leagues L1-L4)\n  - Tests: error handling (404 for nonexistent, 400 for invalid sport)\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:41:49Z] [info] Docker Build Success\n- Image built successfully: my_test_image_1\n- Quarkus started in 2.820s\n- DataInitializer seeded leagues successfully\n- Installed features: agroal, cdi, hibernate-orm, jdbc-h2, narayana-jta, rest, rest-jackson, smallrye-context-propagation, smallrye-health, vertx\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:42:00Z] [info] Smoke Tests Passed\n- All 19 tests passed\n- Results: 19 passed, 0 failed, 19 total\n- Tested endpoints: health, leagues, teams, players, queries\n- All CRUD operations functional\n- All query endpoints functional\n- Data seeding verified\n- Error handling verified\n\n## [2026-03-17T01:42:10Z] [info] Migration Complete\n- Framework: Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) -> Quarkus 3.17.8\n- Build: Multi-module EAR -> Single uber-JAR\n- Runtime: Open Liberty 24.0.0.12 -> Quarkus 3.17.8 on JVM\n- All REST API endpoints preserved and functional\n- All business logic preserved\n- Data seeding preserved\n- No compilation errors\n- No runtime errors\n- All smoke tests passing\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":467,"cache_read_input_tokens":107572,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":467,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3287},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d48893e1-9e26-43a0-bfcb-cd1badbcc494","uuid":"b6ae4c88-3ffe-4e2c-8508-9483bb75b93a"}
