nScoped with @Observes StartupEvent\n- src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/RosterResource.java: JAX-RS with @Inject\n- src/main/java/jakartaee/tutorial/roster/web/RosterApplication.java: JAX-RS Application\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/roster/util/*.java: DTOs and exception (4 files)\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Quarkus config (H2, Hibernate, port)\n- smoke.py: 19 smoke tests for all REST endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Complete migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- roster-common/ (entire module)\n- roster-ejb/ (entire module)\n- roster-web/ (entire module)\n- roster-appclient/ (entire module)\n- roster-ear/ (entire module)\n- All JSF beans (PlayerBean, LeagueBean, TeamBean)\n- All XHTML views (player.xhtml, team.xhtml, league.xhtml)\n- web.xml, beans.xml, persistence.xml, server.xml\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T01:34:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure: 5-module Jakarta EE EAR on Open Liberty\n[2026-03-17T01:34:30Z] [info] Designed migration strategy: flatten to single Quarkus module\n[2026-03-17T01:35:00Z] [info] Created new pom.xml with Quarkus BOM 3.17.8\n[2026-03-17T01:35:30Z] [info] Created flat src/main/java directory structure\n[2026-03-17T01:36:00Z] [info] Migrated 5 entity classes (field-based JPA, SINGLE_TABLE inheritance)\n[2026-03-17T01:36:30Z] [info] Migrated RequestBean: @Stateful -> @ApplicationScoped, EJBException -> RuntimeException\n[2026-03-17T01:36:45Z] [info] Migrated DataInitializer: @Singleton/@Startup -> @Observes StartupEvent\n[2026-03-17T01:37:00Z] [info] Migrated Request interface: removed @Remote\n[2026-03-17T01:37:15Z] [info] Migrated RosterResource: @EJB -> @Inject\n[2026-03-17T01:37:30Z] [info] Copied DTO classes (PlayerDetails, TeamDetails, LeagueDetails, IncorrectSportException)\n[2026-03-17T01:38:00Z] [info] Created application.properties (H2, Hibernate drop-and-create, port 8080)\n[2026-03-17T01:38:15Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile for Quarkus uber-jar\n[2026-03-17T01:38:30Z] [info] Generated smoke.py with 19 tests\n[2026-03-17T01:39:00Z] [info] Removed old module directories\n[2026-03-17T01:41:49Z] [info] Docker build and start successful (Quarkus in 2.8s)\n[2026-03-17T01:42:00Z] [info] All 19 smoke tests passed\n[2026-03-17T01:43:00Z] [info] Created CHANGELOG.md\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors encountered during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Mitigation Steps:** N/A\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None - migration is complete and fully functional"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":980,"cache_read_input_tokens":112398,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":980,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1454},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d48893e1-9e26-43a0-bfcb-cd1badbcc494","uuid":"d3f03efe-7c67-481c-8d30-bc99a8f8c177"}
